txt.en: Cartographile -- Moria
You collected the map of the Walls of Moria
Also called Hollin Gate, this map shows the area surrounding the entrance to Moria.
You have obtained the map of the Silvertine Lodes
This is a map of the area of Moria that the dwarves call the Silvertine Lodes.
You have obtained a map of Durin's Way
This map shows the main thoroughfare of Moria, also called Durin's Way.
